            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Icuayo cuahuitl zo xihuitl, tlen eli ica huahcapan zo tlaltzintlan, nochipa mozcaltia ica huahcapan huan axcanah quence inelhuayo tlen mozcaltia ica tlaltzintlan, ni nochipa pantlatzquitoc ixihuiyo, ixochiyo huan itlacca.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
